readable.content: A black dog and small white and black dog look up at a kitchen countertop . A large dog and a small dog stand next to the kitchen counter to investigate . a small black and white dog standing next to a large black dog both looking up onto a counter . Dogs ignore plate of food on floor , look up at kitchen counter . The dogs are begging at the kitchen counter .
